-----BEGIN PGP SIGNED MESSAGE-----

My patch 3048 contained a small bug, in that its method of checking for
an attempt to change the type of a special parameter is ineffective.
The commands

typeset -R UID
echo $UID

will cause a crash without this patch.

 -zefram

